    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience perfection with this breathtaking, showroom-ready vehicle that looks and feels brand new! This car is in truly mint condition, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that still has that fresh, off-the-lot feel. It drives like a dream and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. If you're looking for a vehicle that is essentially indistinguishable from a new one, this is the one for you!",
