    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine struggles to idle consistently and the transmission shows clear signs of slipping during gear changes. Additionally, the exterior has several noticeable dents and the interior upholstery is heavily worn. This car is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source for parts.",
